<h1 id="welcome">Welcome to Book Swap</h1>

<p>Build a bookshelf of books to trade to other users in exchange for points that you can use to get more books!</p>
<p>The only cost is shipping when you're sending a book.</p>
<p>It's completely up to you whether you keep the book you receive or if you put it up for trading after you're done.
   Every user gets a few points to get them started and then you get more when you've successfully traded a book.
</p>

<form id="returningUser">
  <fieldset>
    <legend>Complete the below fields to login to an existing account</legend>
    <br>
    <label for="accountname"> Username:
        <input id="username" name="name" type="text" placeholder="Enter Username" required>
    </label>
    <br>
    <label for="pw"> Password:
        <input id="password" name="pw" type="password" placeholder="Enter Password" required>
    </label>
    <br>
    <br>
    <input id="userLogin" type="submit" name="login" value="Click Here to Login!">
    <br>
    <p>Or <a href="/signup">click here</a> to create a new account!</p>
  </fieldset>
</form>

